Wow… no shouts for this masterpiece?!?!?!? Sure, this is a bit different from the rest of the material on the disc but that only makes it stand out even more as one of the most heartfelt tunes penned by Bob and the boys. A little sad, really sweet and magnificent listen after listen. Brings tears to my eyes it’s so damn good.
